A '''merchant''' is a person who trades in products and commodities to amass wealth. Regardless of their origins, merchants can amass enough wealth allowing to attain power and influence.

Cities such as [[Pentos]], [[Qarth]], and [[Astapor]] are ruled by elites of wealthy merchants. Some of these merchants, particularly those of [[Slaver's Bay]],Â engage in the international [[Slavery|slave]] trade.
